Dear Prof. Goodwin 
 
First of all I wish send a big congratulation for you and your team 
to let this powerful sowftware freely available ont the net. But 
unfortunatelly I had not success to compile it under my computer 
which runs Mandrake 10.0. Here is attached the stdout and stderr 
result of the configure and make commands.  
 
Another question: I normally run my matlab compatible programs under 
octave or scilab. Could I do also to run cantera under octave or 
scilab? How can I do it? 
 
Tank you for all! 
 
Wladimyr
